      • getEventStats

        List<Stat> getEventStats(String siteId,
                       List<String> events,
                       Date iDate,
                       Date fDate,
                       List<String> userIds,
                       boolean inverseUserSelection,
                       PagingPosition page,
                       List<String> totalsBy,
                       String sortBy,
                       boolean sortAscending,
                       int maxResults)
        Get event statistics (totals by user/event/date).
        Parameters:
        siteId - The site ID (can be null)
        events - List of events to get statistics for (see getPreferences(String, boolean), EventRegistryService) (can be null)
        iDate - The initial date (can be null)
        fDate - The final date (can be null)
        userIds - The list of user Ids (can be null)
        inverseUserSelection - match users not in userIds list
